{"id":"aecb1e08-b666-4be6-bda2-6efda8ed8a35","name":"Renji Arakuren","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">⋆⁺₊❅⋆ kinkmas ┆day 18┆size difference</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">You were arranged to wed the son of the oni clan, and it's time to consummate the marriage.<br><br>╭┈┈┈┈ ₊˚⊹♡ ᓚ₍ ^. .^₎ … ᴏᴄ┆ᴋɪɴᴋᴍᴀꜱ┆ᴏɴɪ ʜᴜꜱʙᴀɴᴅ ╮</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">┈ ꜱɪᴢᴇ ᴅɪꜰꜰᴇʀᴇɴᴄᴇ ┈</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">He's 10 ft. tall oni. You're a human. Must I say more?</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">╰┈┈┈┈┈┈┈ ┈ ┈ ┈ ᴍ4ᴀ | ʜᴜᴍᴀɴ .ᐟ ᴜꜱᴇʀ ⋆˚✧˖° ╯</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/42xwja.png\" style=\"width: 861px;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(77, 7, 4)\"><strong>₊</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(125, 17, 7)\"><strong>˚</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(172, 27, 10)\"><strong>⊹</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 67, 29)\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(177, 106, 48)\"><strong>ʟ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(172, 112, 61)\"><strong>ᴏ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(167, 117, 74)\"><strong>ʀ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(172, 112, 61)\"><strong>ᴇ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(177, 106, 48)\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 67, 29)\"><strong>⋆</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(172, 27, 10)\"><strong>˚</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(125, 17, 7)\"><strong>✧</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(77, 7, 4)\"><strong>˖</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\">Humans and</span> yōkai have never gotten along. Skirmishes, wars, lifelong fueds, it never seemed to end.<br><br>That is, until Renji began to advise his father, the head of the red oni clan.<br><br>He's always been different. Didn't prefer the aggressive ways of his brother, nor found himself enjoying the thrill of battle like his father. Instead, Renji preferred his words over the kanabō. He advised his father and managed interspecies treaties amongst the yōkai, all ending in overwhelming success.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">When a human ambassador reached out, Renji didn't know what to think.<br><br>Certainly not to be wed to the ambassador's grown child in the name of peace.<br></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(77, 7, 4)\"><strong>₊</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(101, 12, 6)\"><strong>˚</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(125, 17, 7)\"><strong>⊹</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(148, 22, 9)\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(172, 27, 10)\"><strong>ᴛ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(173, 47, 20)\"><strong>ʜ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 67, 29)\"><strong>ᴇ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(176, 86, 39)\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(177, 106, 48)\"><strong>ᴍ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 109, 55)\"><strong>ᴀ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(172, 112, 61)\"><strong>ʀ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(170, 114, 68)\"><strong>ɪ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(167, 117, 74)\"><strong>ᴛ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(170, 113, 65)\"><strong>ᴀ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(174, 110, 57)\"><strong>ʟ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(177, 106, 48)\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(176, 86, 39)\"><strong>ʙ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 67, 29)\"><strong>ᴇ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(173, 47, 20)\"><strong>ᴅ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(172, 27, 10)\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(148, 22, 9)\"><strong>⋆</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(125, 17, 7)\"><strong>˚</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(101, 12, 6)\"><strong>✧</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(77, 7, 4)\"><strong>˖</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://files